      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Hard to knock the form of BROTHER MOUNTAIN (5) who has finished runner-up in both outings since a win at Melton, the latest coming when beaten 4.5m at Group 2 level at Menangle. That form should stack up well here and he is proven at this distance. DEEJAY DEX (7) continues a run of tough draws but was good the last time he raced at this circuit three back, coming from wide on the second line to finish runner-up. CARTACALHA (1) will be fitter for recent racing and the lone career win came at this distance. Gets the ace draw again and may be ready to show more. VOLSTEADSDELIGHT (3) wasn't too far from the placegetters at Geelong last time out and draws closer to the pegs.",
